mage = Elijah Daniel.jpeg\n| image_size = 220px\n| caption = Daniel in January 2014\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1994|1|9}}\n| birth_place = [[Detroit]], [[Michigan]], U.S.\n| residence = [[Los Angeles]], [[California]]\n| occupation = {{hlist|Internet personality|comedian|jackson jacobs' biggest fan and worst rival|rapper|record producer|writer}}\n| yearsactive = 2011\u2013present\n| known_for = ''Trump Temptations'' (2016)<ref name=dyer /><ref name=\"gqmagazine\">{{citation|last=Moore|first=Jack|title=Politics - The 9 Best Quotes from the Erotic Donald Trump eBook That's Blowing Up on Amazon|date=January 25, 2016|url=https://www.gq.com/story/trump-temptation-best-lines|work=[[GQ (magazine)|GQ]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170131074508/http://www.gq.com/story/trump-temptation-best-lines|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=January 31, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"racheldicker\">{{citation|last=Dicker|first=Rachel|title=A Gay Erotica Novella About Donald Trump Is an Amazon Best-Seller - Let 'Trump Temptations' sweep you away.|date=January 28, 2016|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2016-01-28/a-gay-erotica-novella-about-donald-trump-is-an-amazon-best-seller|work=[[U.S. News & World Report]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214063824/http://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2016-01-28/a-gay-erotica-novella-about-donald-trump-is-an-amazon-best-seller|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=February 14, 2016}}</ref>\n| title = Mayor of [[Hell, Michigan]] <small>(former)</small>\n| awards = [[9th Shorty Awards|Best Comedian]], [[Shorty Awards]] (2017)<ref name=shortyawards /><ref name=hollywoodreportershorty /><ref name=varietyshorty />\n| website = \n| module             = {{Infobox musical artist|embed=yes\n| background         = solo_singer\n| instrument         = Vocals\n| genre              = Hip hop\n| associated_acts    = {{hlist|Adam&Steve|Dr. Woke|[[Tana Mongeau]]|[[CupcakKe|cupcakKe]] |}}\n| label              = {{hlist|Independent}}\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Elijah Daniel''' (born January 9, 1994) is an American [[comedian]], [[rapper]], [[music producer|record producer]], [[songwriter]], and [[author]]. He became popular [[Online and offline|online]] through his [[satire|satirical]] [[social media]] posts.<ref name=\"dyer\">{{citation|last=Andrews-Dyer|first=Helena|title=The 7 best punchlines from the Trump erotica e-book that's currently No. 1 on Amazon|date=January 26, 2016|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2016/01/26/the-7-best-punchlines-from-the-trump-erotica-e-book-thats-currently-no-1-on-amazon/|work=[[The Washington Post]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716154623/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2016/01/26/the-7-best-punchlines-from-the-trump-erotica-e-book-thats-currently-no-1-on-amazon/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=July 16, 2017}}</ref><ref name=binderpaper /><ref name=orfanides /> Daniel began rapping under the name '''Lil Phag''' in late 2017.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.elevatormag.com/elijah-daniel-is-now-lil-phag-and-he-just-dropped-a-new-music-video/|title=Elijah Daniel is now LIL PHAG, and he just dropped a new music video {{!}} ELEVATOR|date=2017-12-02|work=ELEVATOR|access-date=2018-01-07|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://studybreaks.com/culture/music/lil-phag-elijah-daniel-lgbtq/|title=Everything You Need to Know About LIL PHAG, the LGBTQ Prankster {{!}} Study Breaks|date=2018-07-01|work=Study Breaks|access-date=2018-07-02|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\nDaniel rose to prominence as the author of the [[erotic novel]] ''Trump Temptations''.<ref name=\"binderfusion\">{{cite web|url=http://fusion.net/story/258101/donald-trump-gay-erotica-amazon-kindle/|title=Talking to the guy who got drunk, wrote Donald Trump gay erotica, and put it on Amazon|last1=Binder|first1=Shawn|date=January 22, 2016|website=[[Fusion.net]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015215002/http://fusion.net/story/258101/donald-trump-gay-erotica-amazon-kindle/|archivedate=October 15, 2016|url-status=live|access-date=July 17, 2017}}</ref>\n\nOutside of his solo work, Daniel is a part of the EDM/Pop act adam&steve alongside fianc\u00e9, Dr. Woke. ''[[Billboard Magazine|Billboard]]'' has dubbed the duo \"the gay [[Chainsmokers]]\". They have since released 6 singles featuring [[Maty Noyes]], Sophie Rose, [[Gnash (musician)|Gnash]], JVZEL, XYL\u00d8, and [[Waterparks (band)|Waterparks]].\n\nHe won the award for Best Comedian with collaborator Christine Sydelko at the [[9th Shorty Awards]].<ref name=hollywoodreportershorty/><ref name=varietyshorty /><ref name=shortyawards />\n==Early life==\nElijah Daniel was born in Detroit, Michigan. He was raised as an evangelical Christian. After his grandmother became ill, Daniel moved into her residence to care for her.<ref name=binderpaper /> During this period, he began to write comedy to occupy himself.<ref name=binderpaper /> He publicized his comedy work through posts on [[Twitter]]. <ref name=binderpaper /> <ref name=ohara>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=https://www.dailydot.com/unclick/amazon-reviews-donald-trump-fanfic-billionaire-bellboy/|work=[[The Daily Dot]]|title=This drunk guy's hot gay Donald Trump fanfic is making America horny again|first=Mary Emily|last=O'Hara|date=January 27, 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805102222/https://www.dailydot.com/unclick/amazon-reviews-donald-trump-fanfic-billionaire-bellboy/|archivedate=August 5, 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n===2013\u201316: Career beginnings===\n;White House petition\nDaniel led an [[We the People (petitioning system)|online White House petition]] in 2013 to make the [[Miley Cyrus]] song \"[[Party in the U.S.A.]]\" the U.S. [[national anthem]].<ref name=ohara /><ref name=hpde /> It received international coverage.{{r|petition}} Starting in 2014, he began hosting a weekly internet prank with [[CollegeHumor]] called Text Prank Thursday, where he would have his [[Twitter]] followers text random phone numbers saying whatever he told them to say.<ref>{{cite web|access-date=July 18, 2017|date=March 6, 2014|last1=Daniel|first1=Elijah|title=Epic Twitter Prank: What Happens When You Text a Stranger \"Your Girlfriend Needs to Know About Us\"|url=http://www.collegehumor.com/post/6957047/epic-twitter-prank-what-happens-when-you-text-a-stranger-your-girlfriend-needs-to-know-about-us|website=[[CollegeHumor]]|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614233336/http://www.collegehumor.com/post/6957047/epic-twitter-prank-what-happens-when-you-text-a-stranger-your-girlfriend-needs-to-know-about-us|archivedate=June 14, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Grant|first1=Hannah|title=Text Prank Thursday: What Happens When You Tell A Stranger You Slept With His Girlfriend|url=http://www.collegehumor.com/post/6958619/text-prank-thursday-what-happens-when-you-tell-a-stranger-you-slept-with-his-girlfriend|website=[[CollegeHumor]]|access-date=July 18, 2017|date=March 13, 2014|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412144800/http://www.collegehumor.com/post/6958619/text-prank-thursday-what-happens-when-you-tell-a-stranger-you-slept-with-his-girlfriend|archivedate=April 12, 2016}}</ref> Daniel told [[Vice (magazine)|Vice]] that he cultivated a group of followers online who appreciated his absurd and bizarre comedic antics.<ref name=hpde /> By 2016, his Twitter following had grown to over 95,000.<ref name=dyer /><ref name=\"donohoe\">{{citation|last=Donohoe|first=Rose|title=Donald Trump stars in 'sensual and tawdry' erotic novel|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://thenewdaily.com.au/entertainment/books/2016/01/27/donald-trump-stars-sensual-tawdry-erotic-novel/|work=The New Daily|access-date=July 18, 2017}}</ref><ref name=roberttait>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/donald-trump/12124014/Gay-erotic-novel-about-Donald-Trump-becomes-overnight-hit.html|work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]|title=Gay-erotic novel about Donald Trump becomes overnight hit|date=January 27, 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603165110/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/donald-trump/12124014/Gay-erotic-novel-about-Donald-Trump-becomes-overnight-hit.html|archivedate=June 3, 2016}}</ref>\n\n;Work with Sydelko\nIn January 2017, Daniel and Sydelko released a parody video of the song \"[[Closer (The Chainsmokers song)|Closer]]\" originally by [[The Chainsmokers]], featuring [[Halsey (singer)|Halsey]].<ref name=grannum>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=http://www.inquisitr.com/4032535/halsey-claps-back-at-youtuber-for-bingbong-parody-video-mocking-her-fans/|work=Inquisitr|date=March 4, 2017|title=Halsey claps back at YouTuber for 'Bingbong' parody video, mocking her fans|first=Patricia|last=Grannum|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729232129/http://www.inquisitr.com/4032535/halsey-claps-back-at-youtuber-for-bingbong-parody-video-mocking-her-fans/|archivedate=July 29, 2017}}</ref> The video prompted a response from Halsey, who criticized the parody and Daniel and Sydelko's supporters.<ref name=grannum />\n\n;Television pilots\nBased on the press he received for his book, Daniel was able to sell two TV series proposals.<ref name=hpde /><ref name=\"micnumberone\">{{citation|last=Solis|first=Marie|title=New Erotic Novella 'Trump Temptation' Is Probably a Great Beach Read \u2014 If You're Into That|date=January 27, 2016|url=https://mic.com/articles/133681/new-erotic-novella-trump-temptation-is-probably-a-great-beach-read-if-you-re-into-that|work=[[Mic (media company)|Mic]]|quote=As of this writing, the book is No. 1 on both Amazon's 'gay erotica' and 'humorous erotica' bestseller lists.|access-date=July 18, 2017}}</ref><ref name=pridela>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=https://thepridela.com/2016/01/viral-trump-erotica-author-sells-two-tv-shows/|work=The Pride LA|title=Viral Trump Erotica Author Sells two TV Shows|date=January 26, 2016}}</ref> In conjunction with production firm PR\u00d8HBTD, Daniel was given roles of actor, producer, and creator of the two series.<ref name=binderpaper /> These included one [[docu-series]] titled ''Elijah Daniel is Insane'', and one scripted [[comedy]] titled ''Social'' co-starring Vine [[comedian]] Christine Sydelko.<ref name=dyer /><ref name=binderpaper>{{cite web|access-date=July 17, 2017|date=January 26, 2016|last1=Binder|first1=Shawn|title=Catching Up With Elijah Daniel on His Viral Trump Erotic Novel|url=http://www.papermag.com/elijah-daniel-donald-trump-erotica-1572908332.html|work=[[Paper (magazine)|Paper]]|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210135355/http://www.papermag.com/elijah-daniel-donald-trump-erotica-1572908332.html|archivedate=December 10, 2016}}</ref> In October 2016, FOTV Media Networks Inc. announced a business partnership with Daniel and Sydelko to produce a full season of their series ''Trash, Talking''.<ref name=jeffstevens>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=http://www.shockya.com/news/2016/10/12/does-donald-trump-have-the-midas-touch/|title=Does Donald Trump Have The Midas Touch?|first=Jeff|last=Stevens|date=October 12, 2016|work=Shockya|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719193431/http://www.shockya.com/news/2016/10/12/does-donald-trump-have-the-midas-touch/|archivedate=July 19, 2017}}</ref><ref name=comedyduo>{{citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/comedy-duo-who-got-arrested-throwing-sex-toy-at-trump-get-live-show-on-fotv-2165667.htm|date=October 11, 2016|title=Comedy Duo Who Got Arrested Throwing Sex Toy at Trump Get Live Show on FOTV|work=MarketWired|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015091235/http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/comedy-duo-who-got-arrested-throwing-sex-toy-at-trump-get-live-show-on-fotv-2165667.htm|archivedate=October 15, 2016}}</ref>\n\n=== 2016\u201318: Political stunts and media attention ===\n;''Trump Temptations''\nIn 2016, Daniel stated on Twitter that he was going to get drunk and write an [[erotic novel]] starring [[Donald Trump]].<ref name=\"racheldicker\" /><ref name=\"nagesh\">{{citation|last=Nagesh|first=Ashitha|title=Someone wrote an erotic novel all about Donald Trump and you can now buy it on Amazon|date=January 22, 2016|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/01/22/someone-wrote-an-erotic-novel-all-about-donald-trump-and-you-can-now-buy-it-on-amazon-5638710/|work=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro News]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404103515/http://metro.co.uk/2016/01/22/someone-wrote-an-erotic-novel-all-about-donald-trump-and-you-can-now-buy-it-on-amazon-5638710/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=April 4, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"outmag\">{{citation|last=Brathwaite|first=Les Fabian|title=Gay Erotic Novella Starring Donald Trump Becomes #1 Bestseller|date=January 26, 2016|url=https://www.out.com/popnography/2016/1/26/gay-erotic-novella-starring-donald-trump-1-bestseller|work=[[Out (magazine)|Out]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308033614/http://www.out.com/popnography/2016/1/26/gay-erotic-novella-starring-donald-trump-1-bestseller|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=March 8, 2016}}</ref> Daniel was inspired by a tweet which said the user wished to perform a sex act on [[Bernie Sanders]].<ref name=\"binderfusion\" /><ref name=\"donohoe\" /> He wrote the work as a parody of ''[[Fifty Shades of Grey]]''.<ref name=\"christaylor\">{{Citation|last=Taylor|first=Chris|title=Trump erotica vs. Cruz erotica: Who wins the primary of porn?|date=January 22, 2016|url=http://mashable.com/2016/01/22/trump-cruz-erotica-porn-primary/|work=[[Mashable]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201103956/http://mashable.com/2016/01/22/trump-cruz-erotica-porn-primary//|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=December 1, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"bhutia\">{{citation|last=Bhutia|first=Jigmey|title=Donald Trump gay erotic novel tops Amazon charts|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/donald-trump-gay-erotic-novel-tops-amazon-charts-1540293|work=[[International Business Times]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316051219/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/donald-trump-gay-erotic-novel-tops-amazon-charts-1540293|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=March 16, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"standard\">{{citation|last=Butter|first=Susannah|title=How the internet trumped Donald Trump with cat combovers and erotica|date=January 27, 2016|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/how-the-internet-trumped-donald-trump-with-cat-combovers-and-erotica-a3166231.html|work=[[London Evening Standard]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127140847/http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/how-the-internet-trumped-donald-trump-with-cat-combovers-and-erotica-a3166231.html|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=January 27, 2016}}</ref> Within four hours, he had released the erotic novel titled ''Trump Temptations: The Billionaire & The Bellboy'' on Amazon.<ref name=\"ryanbarrell\">{{citation|last=Barrell|first=Ryan|title='Trump Temptation: The Billionaire And The Bellboy' Is The Donald Trump Erotic Novel You Never Knew You Needed|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2016/01/26/donald-trump-erotic-novel-trump-temptation-the-billionaire-and-the-bellboy_n_9076134.html|work=[[The Huffington Post]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324120952/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2016/01/26/donald-trump-erotic-novel-trump-temptation-the-billionaire-and-the-bellboy_n_9076134.html|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=March 24, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"marcshapiro\">{{citation|last=Shapiro|first=Marc|title=Trump This!: The Life and Times of Donald Trump, An Unauthorized Biography|page=80|year=2016|publisher=Riverdale Avenue Books|isbn=978-1626012646}}</ref><ref name=\"nickduffy\">{{citation|last=Duffy|first=Nick|title=Someone wrote gay erotica about Donald Trump and it's as bad as you think|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2016/01/26/someone-wrote-gay-erotica-about-donald-trump-and-its-as-bad-as-you-think/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531170737/http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2016/01/26/someone-wrote-gay-erotica-about-donald-trump-and-its-as-bad-as-you-think/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=May 31, 2016}}</ref> This was Daniel's [[debut novel]].<ref>{{citation|last=Gauthier|first=Brendan|title='Leathery yet frigid flesh of a privileged and hypocritical billionaire': The Amazon reviews for Donald Trump gay erotica satire are amazing|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.salon.com/2016/01/26/leathery_yet_frigid_flesh_of_a_privileged_and_hypocritical_billionaire_the_amazon_reviews_for_donald_trump_gay_erotica_satire_are_amazing/|work=[[Salon.com|Salon]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316024159/http://www.salon.com/2016/01/26/leathery_yet_frigid_flesh_of_a_privileged_and_hypocritical_billionaire_the_amazon_reviews_for_donald_trump_gay_erotica_satire_are_amazing/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=March 16, 2017}}</ref>\n\n''Trump Temptations'' became the number one best seller on Amazon.com in three categories: humorous erotica, LGBT erotica, and gay erotica.<ref name=\"micnumberone\" /><ref name=\"theweek\">{{citation|title=Erotic Donald Trump novella tops Amazon charts|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.theweek.co.uk/68933/erotic-donald-trump-novella-tops-amazon-charts|work=[[The Week]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170509115751/http://www.theweek.co.uk/68933/erotic-donald-trump-novella-tops-amazon-charts|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=May 9, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"mediaite\">{{citation|last=Ellefson|first=Lindsey|title=Amazon Customers Make Erotica Great Again by Making Sexy Trump Novella Top E-Book|date=January 26, 2016|url=http://www.mediaite.com/online/amazon-customers-make-erotica-great-again-by-making-sexy-trump-novella-top-e-book/|work=[[Mediaite]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731145337/http://www.mediaite.com/online/amazon-customers-make-erotica-great-again-by-making-sexy-trump-novella-top-e-book/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=July 31, 2017}}</ref> The book was listed on Amazon above ''Fifty Shades of Grey'' by [[E. L. James]],<ref name=\"hpde\" /> and was featured in ''[[The Washington Post]]'',<ref name=\"dyer\" /> ''[[Los Angeles Times]]'',<ref name=\"schaub\">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/books/jacketcopy/la-et-jc-donald-trump-erotica-novel-huuuge-amazon-hit-20160126-story.html|title=Donald Trump erotica novel is a huuuge hit on Amazon|last1=Schaub|first1=Michael|date=January 26, 2017|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170603191154/http://www.latimes.com/books/jacketcopy/la-et-jc-donald-trump-erotica-novel-huuuge-amazon-hit-20160126-story.html|archivedate=June 3, 2017|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017}}</ref> ''[[GQ]]'',<ref name=\"gqmagazine\" /> ''[[Gay Star News]]'',<ref name=\"gaystarnews\">{{citation|last=Morgan|first=Joe|title=The 7 most hilarious lines from the gay kinky sex novel about Donald Trump|date=January 27, 2016|url=https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/gay-novella-donald-trump/|work=[[Gay Star News]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318005618/http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/gay-novella-donald-trump/|url-status=live|access-date=July 18, 2017|archivedate=March 18, 2016}}</ref> ''[[Evening Standard|London Evening Standard]]'',<ref name=\"standard\" /> ''[[The Daily Telegraph]]'',<ref name=\"roberttait\" /> and ''[[Vice (magazine)|Vice]]''.<ref name=\"mcmanus\">{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/read/meet-the-comedian-who-wrote-a-hit-erotic-novella-starring-donald-trump|title