riter\n|FOTV Media Networks Inc.<ref name=jeffstevens /><ref name=comedyduo />\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Artist\n! scope=\"col\" | Director\n! scope=\"col\" | Notes\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2013\n| \"[[Badman (EP)|Badman]]\" || [[B.A.P (South Korean band)|B.A.P]] || Hong Won-ki of [[ZanyBros]] || <ref>{{citation|year=2013|title=Badman|publisher=[[B.A.P (South Korean band)|B.A.P]]|first=Hong|last=Won-ki|title-link=Badman (EP)}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2017\n|\"Bing Bong\" <small>(\"[[Closer (Chainsmokers song)|Closer]]\" parody)</small> || Elijah Daniel & Christine Sydelko || Tom Harlock || <ref name=grannum /><ref>{{citation|year=2017|first=Tom|last=Harlock|publisher=Elijah Daniel & Christine Sydelko |agency=YouTube|title=Bing Bong: Official Video, Closer by the Chainsmokers & Halsey Parody}}</ref>\n|-\n!2017\n|\"[[Young Dumb & Broke]]\"\n|[[Khalid]]\n|\n|<ref>{{Citation|last=KhalidVEVO|title=Khalid - Young Dumb & Broke (Official Video)|date=2017-08-01|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IPfJnp1guPc|accessdate=2017-08-09}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Tours==\n;Headlining\n* Probably A Terrible Rap Matinee Tour (2018) (with Dr. Woke)\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Shorty Awards]]\n| [[9th Shorty Awards|Best Comedian]]\n| Elijah Daniel & Christine Sydelko - Winner in Comedy\n| {{Won}}\n| <ref name=shortyawards>{{Citation|access-date=July 18, 2017|url=http://shortyawards.com/9th/elijahdaniel|title=From the 9th Annual Shorty Awards - Elijah Daniel & Christine Sydelko - Winner in Comedy|work=[[9th Shorty Awards|9th Annual Shorty Awards]]|agency=[[Shorty Awards]]|date=April 23, 2017|archivedate=June 6, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606074000/http://shortyawards.com/9th/elijahdaniel}}</ref><ref name=varietyshorty>{{citation|url=https://variety.com/2017/digital/